    elimne0 $p |- ded ( A =/= 0_10 , A , 1_10 ) =/= 0_10 $=
      ( cn0 wne cn1 cded neeq1 ax1ne0 elimhyp ) ABCZIADEZBCDBCADAJBFDJBFGH $.
      $([15-May-99]$)

