       theorems ~ subcl and ~subrcl prove its closure laws. s$)
    df-sub $a |- - = { <. <. x , y >. , z >. |
                   ( ( x e. CC /\ y e. CC ) /\
                   z = U. { w e. CC | ( y + w ) = x } ) } $.
